descriptionHTML:
Model Number: FR-A05

Have a look at the First Edition of Frillroid's FR-A05 Analogue Watchface

If you are a fan of a classic and elegant analogue watch then luxurious Smart Outlook Watchface FR-A05 is just made for you. This watch face is designed keeping in mind the classic look for all of your smart watches like Moto 360, Zen and others. It has analogue design that displays variety of features, getting rid of your hassle of taking out and putting back in your mobile phone.

• Analogue view of time and Date
• Beautiful blue background
• Remaining battery life of your device so you exactly know when to charge

This watch face is designed for round and square display watches so you can use it with any android smart watch.

How it works
It’s simple just download the app to your smartphone and sync it with the watch. The watch face that you will choose will be displayed on your watch screen.
recentChanges: Now compatible with all size devices
